Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:53.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}說實話不太懂什麼味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:58.66,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}因為普普通通毫無刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:05.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}光明的未來混入虛無感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}事情不斷惡化變得混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.30,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}對此早已厭煩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}想要轉生重來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:23.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}就算失敗多次也要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}因為作為人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:31.69,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}就算失敗了好像也不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}好像也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.49,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}無聊聊聊聊聊的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:40.33,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}需要革舊&立新
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:45.46,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}「認真活下去就能改變」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:52.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}疼痛痛痛痛痛全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}它在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:59.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}如果感到厭倦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:04.56,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}那就  革舊&立新
