Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.60,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Bleed my heart dry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.60,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Leave me here to die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.69,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’ll be all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Said, “gimme your heart”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:36.73,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}So I filled it up with all of my love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:40.11,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Gave it to you, trusted that you would keep it safe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.66,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It thrived upon your vibe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Beating in sync with yours at night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:49.66,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You poured your soul into mine with just a wink
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.50,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}So why don’t you want my heart no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’s gathering dust on your bedroom floor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.97,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Do what you want, decision’s yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:00.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I’ll be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:03.64,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}If you won’t take it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:07.60,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You might as well bleed it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:08.85,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Squeeze it like a lemon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:10.81,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Like a rag you’ll throw away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.65,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Bleed my heart dry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:16.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Leave me here to die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.78,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’ll be all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.78,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I know you’ll do what’s right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:26.70,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}And be right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.50,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Won’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.87,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why won’t, why won’t you bleed my heart dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:35.54,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why don’t you leave me here to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:38.80,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why won’t you bleed my heart dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:41.01,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You know that I’ll put it all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:44.97,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I trust you’ll know just what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:50.18,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I’ll be right here, forever waiting for you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.60,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}榨乾我的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.60,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}留我一人等死
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.69,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}全都是因為你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.94,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你說“給我你的心”
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.94,0:21:36.73,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}於是我用全部的愛將其填滿
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.73,0:21:40.11,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}把它給你  相信你會保管好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.66,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}它在你的薰陶下蓬勃
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}在夜晚與你心跳同步
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.83,0:21:49.66,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你只用眨眼就讓我魂牽夢繞
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.50,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}為什麼你不再想要我的心了？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}它在你的臥室地板積灰
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.97,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}做你想做的  都取決於你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.97,0:22:00.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我沒事的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:03.64,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}如果你不接受它
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.64,0:22:07.60,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}或許也會榨乾它
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.60,0:22:08.85,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}像擠壓一個檸檬
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.85,0:22:10.81,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}像一塊無用抹布
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.65,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}榨乾我的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.65,0:22:16.94,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}留我一人等死
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.73,0:22:20.78,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}全都是因為你
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.78,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我知道你會做正確的事
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.78,0:22:26.70,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}陪在我的身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.50,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}對嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.87,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}為什麼你不榨乾我的心臟？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.87,0:22:35.54,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}為什麼你不留我一人等死？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.54,0:22:38.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}為什麼你不榨乾我的心臟？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.80,0:22:41.01,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你知道我會全部交給你
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.01,0:22:44.97,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我相信你知道該做什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.55,0:22:50.18,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我會在這裡  永遠等著你
